value.name: Saint X
value.overview: A young woman's mysterious death during an idyllic Caribbean vacation creates a traumatic ripple effect that eventually pulls her surviving sister into a dangerous pursuit of the truth.

value.name: Roaming China with Tang Poetry
value.overview: After a near-drowning incident, modern woman Chu Ci becomes fate-bound to the time-traveling poet Du Fu. To break the bond, she must accompany him on a journey through historical sites, experiencing Tang poetry and culture. Along the way, their growing friendship transforms their perspectives on life and destiny.
